startUp()
getNextSchedule()...
...getNextSchedule()
SERVICE LISTENER : Running
runOneIteration()
getNextSchedule()...
Stopping service
getNextSchedule() - not running anymore so don't return scheduler
```

notice that there is no "shutDown()" or "Bye" output line.
